== MILHIST initial assessment ==
B class.  Nice work and hope you develop it further.  One problem is the heading photo, which is captioned as being of the battle of Bannockburn.  Although repeated in a number of history books, this isn't true.  It actually depicts an apocalyptic battle.  See the commentary on this folio here http://posner.library.cmu.edu/Posner/books/pages.cgi?call=741.64_H35H_1954&layout=vol0/part0/copy0&file=0258 [[User:Monstrelet|Monstrelet]] ([[User talk:Monstrelet|talk]]) 10:17, 9 April 2012 (UTC)
:Thanks for that. It also shows you shouldn't believe the summaries you read (and also I should have worked this out from a the fact that it was in a bible). I will go sort that one out. I would quite like to get this one up to GA standard, so any advice on improvement is very welcome.--'''<span style="font-family:Black Chancery;text:grey 0.3em 0.3em 0.1em;">[[User:Sabrebd|<span style="color:blue;">SabreBD</span>]] ([[User talk:Sabrebd|talk</span>]]) 11:01, 9 April 2012 (UTC)

